model.query:
from(bucket: "example")
	|> range(start: -1h)
  |> filter(fn: (r) => r["_measurement"] == "user-clicks")
  |> group(columns: ["sessionId"])
  |> count()
  |> rename(columns: {_value: "clicks"})
  |> filter(fn: (r) => r.clicks > 5)
  |> group()
  |> keep(columns: ["sessionId", "clicks"])
  |> yield(name: "over-five-clicks")
